  :caveats-2026-07-16
    ("filter and reduce work per QL 2026-07-16 fix — used freely"
     "physics is REAL where sims require it (conservation, correct integration order)"
     "no corporate names anywhere"
     "publishable-prose doctrine: kid-and-adult readable, dense, honest"
     "compose-orchestrate-in-route-route pattern named at every applicable chapter"))
